</head>
<body>

<div class="header">
    <div class="home-menu pure-menu pure-menu-horizontal pure-menu-fixed">
        <a class="pure-menu-heading" href="/">MediHub</a>

        <ul class="pure-menu-list">
            <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="/" class="pure-menu-link">Home</a></li>
            <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Tour</a></li>
            <li class="pure-menu-item"><a href="#" class="pure-menu-link">Sign Up</a></li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="splash-container">
    <div class="splash">
        <h1 class="splash-head">MediHub</h1>
        <p class="splash-subhead">
            <strong>Diabetic Medication made easy</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
            <a href="/home" class="pure-button pure-button-primary">Get Started</a>
        </p>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="content-wrapper">
    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="content-head is-center">Monitoring Your Medication</h2>

        <div class="pure-g">
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">

                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-user-o"></i>
                    Family always in the loop
                </h3>
                <p>
                 Always know how your elderly loved ones are fairing in combatting their ailments
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-user-secret"></i>
                    Caregiver Oversight
                </h3>
                <p>
                 Making sure your caregivers are giving your eledery loved ones all the attention they need
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-medkit"></i>
                    Improving Medication Compliance
                </h3>
                <p>
                  Elderly people being stubborn, say goodbbye to that with MediHub
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="l-box pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-1-4">
                <h3 class="content-subhead">
                    <i class="fa fa-heart"></i>
                    Assissting your caregiver
                </h3>
                <p>
                 MediHub helps you offer your own input to the caregiver, helping you create an optimal care experience for your elderies
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="ribbon l-box-lrg pure-g">
        <div class="l-box-lrg is-center pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-2-5">
            <img width="300" alt="File Icons" class="pure-img-responsive" src="https://i.ibb.co/tQqD7YC/hands.jpg">
        </div>
        <div class="pure-u-1 pure-u-md-1-2 pure-u-lg-3-5">

            <h2 class="content-head content-head-ribbon">Easing your worries about your elderly loved ones</h2>

            <p>
                MediHub assists you in keeping an eye on your elederly loved ones. Help your caregivers in taking care of your elderly loved ones by offering your own input and advice.
				Remind your elderly loved ones to take their medication so they can live long and fruitful lives.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content">
        <h2 class="content-head is-center">Join MediHub and help your elderly loved ones improve their health</h2>

        <div class="pure-g">
            <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-2-5">
                <form class="pure-form pure-form-stacked">
                    <fieldset>

                        <label for="name">Your Name</label>
                        <input id="name" type="text" placeholder="Your Name">


                        <label for="email">Your Email</label>
                        <input id="email" type="email" placeholder="Your Email">

                        <label for="password">Your Password</label>
                        <input id="password" type="password" placeholder="Your Password">

                        <button type="submit" class="pure-button">Sign Up</button>
                    </fieldset>
                </form>
            </div>

            <div class="l-box-lrg pure-u-1 pure-u-md-3-5">
                <h4>Contact Us</h4>
                <p>
                   Please do not hesitate do give us your feedback. We always appreciate constructive criticism that can help us improve your
				   medical experience.
                </p>

                <h4>More Information</h4>
                <p>
                    For more information, email us at info@medihub.com.hk
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

    </div>

    <div class="footer l-box is-center">
       Made with love by the Team 7.
    </div>

</div>




</body>
</html>
